::Prowl/Firearm/Cledar/Rixer/Forrior/Blyer::

Prowl, Firearm, Cledar, Rixer, Forrior, and Blyer look around at the new surroundings, then looking curiously at Iron Raptor.

"Uh, what do you mean, commander?" Cledar asks, his hand nerviously going for his gun.
